features: 【HIGHT QUALITY MATERIAL】 This utensil holder is made of high-quality stoneware material, ensuring durability and is designed to provide you with a practical and aesthetically pleasing kitchen storage solution. Its unique structure ensures that a large number of spatulas and other kitchen utensils can be securely placed in it without easily tilting or shaking. You can effortlessly store and retrieve the necessary kitchen tools without worrying about them slipping or collapsing.

【DEEP CAPACITY】The product dimensions of 5.2 * 6.2 in (Width *Height ), and it can accommodate 10-15 kitchen utensils, Whether it's spoons, chopsticks, cooking utensils, or other kitchen gadgets, Its moderate size allows it to be easily placed on the kitchen countertop or in the cabinet, making your kitchen surface tidier and easier to use.

【RUSTIC FARMHOUSE DESIGN】 This utensil holder features a matte grinding design in off-white, perfectly showcasing the simplicity and elegance of rustic style. Moreover, the matte finish gives it a smooth touch, providing a comfortable hand feel. Whether in a country-style kitchen or a modern space, this rustic ceramic utensil holder can add a natural and warm atmosphere to your kitchen.

【EASY TO CLEAN】 In addition to its functionality and aesthetics, this vancasso utensil holder is also very easy to clean and maintain. Simply wipe it gently with a mild cleanser and a damp cloth to keep its cleanliness and beautiful appearance. The durability of the ceramic material ensures a long lifespan.

【ELEGANT GIFT】 We hope you can find a unique and meaningful gift to express your love and blessings. This is a perfect choice for holiday gifts, especially suitable for occasions such as Christmas and housewarming celebrations. Whether used as kitchen utensils, decorations, or storage boxes, they can provide your family and friends with a dual enjoyment of practicality and aesthetics.

【GUARANTEE SERVICES】Please check the condition and integrity of the product as soon as you receive it. If you find any issues such as breakage, missing parts, or other quality problems, we encourage you to maintain active communication with our customer service team. We will do our best to provide you with a prompt response and a satisfactory solution.

【ENVIRONMENTALLY FRIENDLY AND HEALTHY】Our cutlery storage containers are made of food-grade materials, non-toxic and odorless, safe and reliable. Your and your family's health is always our top priority!
【MULTIPLE STYLES】We offer a wide range of design styles and different sizes to meet different preferences and decorative needs.
